name: How to Make Spam Musubi
description: In Hawaii, musubis are found at every convenience shop on the islands, 7-11 included. They're sold in school cafeterias and right alongside butter mochi at local bake sales. Picnic? Someone's mom is bound to make at least two dozen. Sleepover? Either dinner that night, or straight out of the fridge for breakfast. It's a ridiculously simple creation, yet its extremely high rating on the scale of tastiness cannot be denied.
